it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.terms
Interface PatternNameTerm

All Superinterfaces:
Term<LSAidValue>, VarTerm<LSAidValue>
All Known Implementing Classes:
PatternNameTermImpl
public interface PatternNameTerm
extends VarTerm<LSAidValue>

This interface models a PatternName inside an Ecolaw, which is a variable that represents an LSA-id for a matching LSA.

It can be a ground, or a (un-)bound variable term.

Author:
Paolo Contessi
